# .claudeignore
# Defines what Claude Code should NOT read in this repository.
# Stack: Java / Spring Boot / Hibernate / PostgreSQL

# ─── Secrets & environment-specific config ────────────────────────────────────
# Keep application.yml and application-dev.yml visible — Claude needs them
# to understand project structure, profiles, and feature flags.
# Ignore only environment-specific overrides that may contain real credentials.
.env
.env.*
**/application-local.*
**/application-prod.*
**/application-staging.*
# TODO: add other profile names used in this project (e.g. application-uat.*)

# ─── Build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Maven
**/target/
# Gradle — TODO: remove if project uses Maven only
**/.gradle/
**/build/

# ─── Generated sources ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Hibernate metamodel, annotation processors (Lombok, MapStruct, etc.)
# **/target/generated-sources/
# **/target/generated-test-sources/

# ─── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# May contain PII, stack traces with sensitive data, or DB dumps
**/logs/
*.log

# ─── IDE & OS noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/.DS_Store
